672,-0.01992438,-0.0714273,0.06050504,-0.02021779,0.04918719,-0.01462283,-0.03709828,0.06578724,0.21648477,0.05147381,0.01548913,-0.00027822,-0.00238893,0.01426925,0.09957907,0.02524178,-0.03141717,-0.0061047,0.0903597,-0.00764068,0.03213679,0.04999278,-0.03212785,0.04379217,0.05549696,-0.00817556,0.04067922,-0.02053461,-0.07256296,0.02123831,0.10287122,0.02492962,-0.0104815,-0.08042507,0.02831542,0.03402568,-0.04048834,-0.01962617,0.00755743,-0.00146028,0.01590563,0.04096564,-0.00666835,-0.03110799,-0.02690907,-0.02540701,0.01073685,0.00505112,0.01114414,0.08746366,0.03643379],"last_embed":{"hash":"1ee3ban","tokens":376}}},"last_read":{"hash":"1ee3ban","at":1769676375507},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1768337484000,"size":18036,"at":1769676327366,"hash":"1ee3ban"},"blocks":{"#":[1,240],"##{1}":[1,1],"##{2}":[2,23],"##{3}":[24,28],"##{4}":[29,34],"##{5}":[35,36],"##{6}":[37,37],"##{7}":[38,38],"##{8}":[39,39],"##{9}":[40,44],"##{10}":[45,45],"##{11}":[46,48],"##{12}":[59,75],"##{13}":[76,79],"##{14}":[80,97],"##{15}":[98,216],"##{16}":[217,240]},"outlinks":[{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":37},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":38},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":46},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":59},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":76},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":80},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":99},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":115},{"title":"1,2)$\n                - (3) $\\left(-\\frac{6}{7}, 4\\right)$\n                - \n            - 解析\n                - (1) 已知 $p(x)=|x-3|, q(x)=4-|x-5|$\n                    - 由 $p(x)<q(x)$ ，即 $|x-3|+|x-5|<4$\n                    - 当 $x \\geq 5$ 时, 不等式化为 $x-3+x-5<4$, 得 $x<6$,\n                    - 此时，不等式的解为 $5 \\leq x<6$ 。\n                    - 当 $3 \\leq x<5$ 时, 不等式化为 $x-3+5-x<4$, 即 $2<4$, 恒成立,\n                    - 此时，不等式的解为 $3 \\leq x<5$ 。\n                    - 当 $x<3$ 时, 不等式化为 $3-x+5-x<4$, 得 $x>2$.\n                    - 此时，不等式的解为 $2<x<3$ 。\n                    - 综上所述, $p(x)<q(x)$ 的解集为 $(2,6)$, 即 $T(p(x), q(x))=(2,6)$.\n                - (2) 由题意知, 不等式 $x-1<(x-a)^{2}+2 a$ (1)恒成立,\n                    - 且不等式 $(x-a)^{2}+2 a<a(x-1)^{2}+62$ 2恒成立;\n                    - 由(1) 得， $x^{2}-(2 a+1) x+\\left(a^{2}+2 a+1\\right)>0$ ，\n                    - 则 $\\Delta=(2 a+1)^{2}-4\\left(a^{2}+2 a+1\\right)<0$, 解得 $a>-\\frac{3}{4}$;\n                    - 由 $(2)$ 得， $(a-1) x^{2}-a^{2}-a+6>0$ ，\n                    - 当 $a=1$ 时，不等式化为 $-1-1+6>0$ 恒成立，\n                    - 当 $a \\neq 1$ 时, 应满足 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}a-1>0 \\\\ -a^{2}-a+6>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 解得 $1<a<2$;\n                    - 综上知, $a$ 的取值范围是 $[1,2)$.\n                - (3) 已知 $f(x)=|2 x-b|, g(x)=\\frac{x+4 b}{x-1}, h(x)=2$,\n                - \n                - 由题意得, 不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解,\n                - 由 $f(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow-2<2 x-b<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{b}{2}-1<x<\\frac{b}{2}+1$,\n                - 又 $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x+4 b}{x-1}<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x+4 b-2(x-1)}{x-1}<0 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x-(4 b+2)}{x-1}>0$,\n                - (1)当 $4 b+2=1$, 即 $b=-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, 上式为 $1>0$, 对任意 $x \\in(-\\infty, 1) \\cup(1,+\\infty)$ 恒成立.此时不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解，满足题意；\n                - (2) 当 $4 b+2<1$, 即 $b<-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow x<4 b+2$ 或 $x>1$,\n                - \n                - 要使不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解, 则 $\\frac{b}{2}-1<4 b+2$ 或 $\\frac{b}{2}+1>1$, 解得 $b>-\\frac{6}{7}$,\n                - 则有 $-\\frac{6}{7}<b<-\\frac{1}{4}$;\n                - (3) 当 $4 b+2>1$, 即 $b>-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow x<1$ 或 $x>4 b+2$.\n                - \n                - 要使不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解,\n                - 则 $\\frac{b}{2}-1<1$ 或 $\\frac{b}{2}+1>4 b+2$, 解得 $b<4$,\n                - 则有 $-\\frac{1}{4}<b<4$ ；\n                - 综上所述, $b$ 的取值范围是 $\\left(-\\frac{6}{7}, 4\\right)$.\n    - \n    - \n    - \n    - ### 集合类似的题目 \n        - > [🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":159},{"title":"🔖","target":"../🔖.md","line":210},{"title":"-1,+\\infty)$$\n\n                  \n- # 学生错题分析\n    - 试听的学生 试卷 \n        - ![","target":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/ENDSly0Ck8HID3SeVmune2u8iUhDV4rVQp8Gp-4KNp0I6qDEOXiFW1eq5tuARxylyRQza5g6VA573K-oENwf8JWbYkQeV46vikZyvQlHoChvv7M7FkK1p-pVMRclcK19.png","line":214}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1ee3ban","at":1769676375174}},"smart_blocks:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/chengbai高中数学框架(承白)/备课集合讲义专题.md##{2}": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08184735,0.00092753,0.06636836,-0.03062219,-0.01697235,-0.00171991,-0.04219233,0.01553291,0.05826695,-0.03129858,0.01677449,-0.07671791,0.06799609,0.01182228,0.02941388,0.00323225,-0.00219708,0.00540913,-0.02965692,-0.0221666,0.10866728,-0.03518367,-0.00366048,-0.06961834,0.05648857,0.03004511,0.00707327,-0.03803458,-0.00607677,-0.20091483,-0.05460586,0.03129556,0.01225635,-0.01296424,0.04245475,-0.04616809,-0.03803921,0.06022938,-0.04369466,0.06211496,0.01439083,0.05656506,0.03635862,-0.00948848,0.0132088,-0.09232598,-0.04680194,0.00155033,0.05157762,-0.01932548,-0.02021402,-0.03378035,0.02615362,0.0555687,-0.0238583,0.03431034,0.0569439,0.00616936,0.0416276,0.03295003,0.06365313,0.03581548,-0.20323479,0.05613665,0.02444302,-0.02161516,-0.01677483,-0.02038294,0.03000629,0.05699821,-0.05074372,0.01101811,-0.04397609,0.04065179,-0.00461383,0.00745962,0.0102219,-0.10791798,-0.07597248,0.01772605,-0.04390997,0.06860362,-0.0663418,0.00270528,0.02866947,0.03997335,-0.0405655,-0.05856739,0.03445909,0.00049921,-0.00827174,-0.04069795,-0.00418422,0.03163137,-0.10914443,-0.03249483,0.04269936,0.01669127,-0.04084548,0.10516187,-0.02476279,0.02585692,-0.03447939,-0.03292513,-0.02062958,0.02139651,-0.04116859,-